{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fedccc153e","title":"毛泽东同邓小平在长沙的一次谈话（节录）","origin":"注：此件是中央办公厅秘书局提供的唐闻生、王海容的记录稿。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"39b689c417","index":0,"year":1974,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"fedccc153e"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2e5fcdeb96","type":"title","text":"同邓小平在长沙的一次谈话（节录）毛泽东（未经邓小平核对）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e"},{"id":"de41c80118","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛对邓小平说）你开了一个钢铁公司！（邓：主席也知道了。）好！（邓：我实在忍不住了，不止一次了。）我赞成你！（邓：她［指江青］在政治局搞了七、八次了。）强加于人哪，我也是不高兴的。她们（用手指王、唐）都不高兴。（邓：我主要是感觉政治局的生活不正常。最后我到她那里去讲了一下，钢铁公司对钢铁公司。）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e"},{"id":"07736799d3","type":"paragraph","text":"这个好。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e"},{"id":"96d2023ab8","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：最近关于我的工作的决定，主席已经讲了，不应再提什么意见了，但是看来责任是太重了一点。）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e"},{"id":"11f8e2160e","type":"paragraph","text":"没办法呢，只好担起来罗 。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e"},{"id":"08fcb9a771","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：此件是中央办公厅秘书局提供的唐闻生、王海容的记录稿。）","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e"}],"page":{"id":"3d11c89957","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fedccc153e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}